{{Infobox Bilateral relations|Greece–Philippines|Greece|Philippines|map=Greece Philippines Locator.png}}

'''Greece''' and the '''Philippines''' established its bilateral, diplomatic and trade relation in 1947. Greece has an embassy in [[Manila]] and the Philippines has an embassy in [[Athens]].

==Economic relations==

The Greek city of [[Thessaloniki]] are open to enhancing business ties with the Philippines. Thessaloniki located in northern Greece, is the country’s second major economic, industrial, commercial and political center, and a major transportation hub for the rest of southeastern Europe.<ref>{{cite web | url= http://business.inquirer.net/73743/greece-local-execs-open-to-enhancing-business-ties-with-ph | title= Greece local execs open to enhancing business ties with PH | work= Inquirer Business | date= 27 July 2012 | accessdate= 23 April 2013}}</ref>

==Migration==

According to official Greek statistics, there were 5,000 Filipinos in Greece in 1991, which declined to 2,000 by 1996. In reality, there were many more [[illegal immigrant|working in the country illegally]].<ref>{{harvnb|Iosifides|King|1999|p=193}}</ref><ref>{{citation|url=http://www.dole.gov.ph/news/details.asp?id=N000000739 |periodical=DOLE News |title=Imson urges Greece-based OFWs to take advantage of new legalization rules |date=2004-06-13 |accessdate=2009-10-23 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160123092632/http://www.dole.gov.ph/news/details.asp?id=N000000739 |archivedate=2016-01-23 |df= }}</ref> The Philippine community have set up a school for their children in downtown [[Athens]].<ref>{{harvnb|Cañete|2004|p=135}}</ref>

A large proportion are women (81% in 1999), who generally find employment as [[domestic worker]]s.<ref>{{harvnb|Iosifides|King|1999|p=194}}</ref>

In 2009 there were 30,000 Filipinos in Greece.<ref>{{citation|url=http://www.athenspe.net/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=57&Itemid=2 |title=Filipino Community |publisher=Philippine Embassy in Athens, Greece and Cyprus |accessdate=2009-10-13 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090617034146/http://www.athenspe.net/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=57&Itemid=2 |archivedate=2009-06-17 |df= }}</ref>

